## 6. Design tokens CSS

Drop-in block for `app/frontend/src/design-tokens.css`. Every value MUST be
copied from § 1 (which in turn cites § 0 screenshots).

```css
:root {
  /* Surfaces */
  --surface-white: #______;
  --surface-gray: #______;
  --canvas-bg: #______;

  /* Primary */
  --primary: #______;
  --primary-hover: #______;
  --primary-text: #______;

  /* Brand */
  --brand-blue: #______;

  /* Text */
  --text-primary: #______;
  --text-secondary: #______;
  --text-muted: #______;
  --text-link: #______;

  /* Borders + radii */
  --border: #______;
  --border-strong: #______;
  --border-radius: 4px;
  --border-radius-card: 8px;
  --border-radius-pill: 999px;

  /* Typography */
  --font-family: "[UI font]", "Roboto", Arial, sans-serif;
  --font-size-xs: 12px;
  --font-size-sm: 13px;
  --font-size-base: 14px;
  --font-size-lg: 16px;
  --font-size-xl: 18px;
  --font-size-2xl: 22px;

  /* Shadows */
  --shadow-card: 0 1px 3px rgba(60,64,67,0.15);
  --shadow-card-hover: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.16);
}
```
